***[#green] <i><size:12><color #white><b>Cloud Storage
****[#yellow] <i><size:12><color #black>Scalable data storage solutions in the cloud <b>(e.g., AWS S3, Azure Blob Storage).
***[#green] <i><size:12><color #white><b>Cloud Compute
